<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy Birthday Akshata</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
background: linear-gradient(135deg,#ff758c,#ff7eb3);
color:white;
text-align:center;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

section{
padding:60px 20px;
}

h1{
font-size:3rem;
animation: glow 2s infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes glow{
from{ text-shadow:0 0 10px #fff;}
to{ text-shadow:0 0 30px #ff0055;}
}

p{
max-width:700px;
margin:auto;
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.6;
}

button{
padding:15px 30px;
font-size:18px;
border:none;
border-radius:30px;
background:white;
color:#ff0055;
cursor:pointer;
margin-top:20px;
}

.hidden{
display:none;
}

.heart{
position:fixed;
font-size:20px;
animation: float 6s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes float{
0%{transform:translateY(100vh);}
100%{transform:translateY(-10vh);}
}

footer{
padding:40px;
font-size:18px;
}

</style>





<section>

<h1>Happy Birthday Akshata ❤️</h1>

<p>
Today is your special day.  
Even if life took us in different directions,  
I still wish happiness, peace, and beautiful moments for you.
</p>

<button onclick="showMessage()">Click to Read My Heart</button>

</section>

<section id="message" class="hidden">

<h2>A Message From My Heart</h2>

<p>
Akshata,

I have loved you for 7 years.  
Life changed, situations changed, and maybe feelings changed too.  
But one thing that never changed in me is the respect and love I still have for you.

Even if you ignore my messages,  
even if I am no longer part of your world,  
my heart still silently wishes that you stay happy forever.

You may never know how deeply you touched my life,  
but you will always remain a beautiful chapter in my story.

On your birthday, I just want to say:

May your life be filled with happiness, success, and smiles.

Happy Birthday Akshata[bangari].
</p>

</section>

<section>

<h2>One Truth</h2>

<p>
Sometimes love doesn't mean being together.  
Sometimes love means wishing someone happiness even when they are not with you.
</p>

</section>

<section>

<button onclick="finalSurprise()">Open Final Message</button>

<h1 id="final" class="hidden">
No matter what happens in life,  
a part of my heart will always care for you. ❤️
</h1>

</section>

<footer>
Made with love and memories
</footer>

<script>

function showMessage(){
document.getElementById("message").classList.remove("hidden")
}

function finalSurprise(){
document.getElementById("final").classList.remove("hidden")
}

function createHeart(){
let heart=document.createElement("div")

heart.className="heart"
heart.innerHTML="❤️"

heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw"
heart.style.fontSize=Math.random()*20+10+"px"

document.body.appendChild(heart)

setTimeout(()=>{
heart.remove()
},6000)

}

setInterval(createHeart,300)

</script>

